I was listening to music in preparing for the first of the year for the experience,

6
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:27,280
the rock and roll experience over here in the gym.

7
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:32,100
And I was kind of listening to various classic rock songs that we're going to be doing,

8
